Package edu.umn.se.trap.db

Class Summary
CurrencyDB Mimics the currency conversion database.
GrantDB Mimics the grant database.
PerDiemDB Mimics the database of meal/incidental per diems.
UserDB Mimics the X500 database.
UserGrantDB Mimics the DB table between the association between the users and the grants.
 

Enum Summary
CurrencyDB.CURRENCY_FIELDS This type enumerates the fields of the ArrayList with the conversion information.
GrantDB.GRANT_FIELDS This type enumerates the fields of the ArrayList with the grant information.
PerDiemDB.RATE_FIELDS This type enumerates the fields of the ArrayList with the per diem information.
UserDB.USER_FIELDS This type enumerates the fields of the ArrayList with the user information.
UserGrantDB.USER_GRANT_FIELDS This type enumerates the fields of the ArrayList with the user information.
 

Exception Summary
KeyNotFoundException Exception that is thrown when a mocked DB key is not found.
